snippet.title: Vital Device/바이탈 디바이스 (Cenozoic) - Abelisys mission 6 "A plot of betrayal"
snippet.description:
Un clon coreano directo de starcraft, claro que en vez de batallas interplanetarias ocurren batallas digestivas dentro de un cuerpo humano. Por eso se recolectan proteinas en vez de minerales.
Solo hay 2 razas, y muy reminiscentes de los zerg y terran.


A lot of people asked me for a download link for this game, so there you go:    https://mega.nz/#!KgM2mYII!0siTfmFq-MiNTVrhDeGIwlA_BJGwKvd7wldSDsd7xpA

Please, understand that you must change the display language in Windows to Korean.

Windows 10: http://www.howtogeek.com/232659/how-to-change-the-display-language-in-windows-10/

Windows 7: http://windows.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-vista/change-the-display-language
